  "body": "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS ANNOUNCES EXPERTBOOK B3 SERIES: Price, Specifications ~ My Mobile ...\" src=\"https://www.mymobileindia.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6_Keyboard-1.webp\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=mymobileindia.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">mymobileindia.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS Unveils 2026 AI-Powered Portfolio at CES, including ExpertBook ...\" src=\"https://press.asus.com/assets/w_1266,h_844/cfd2f47e-31a2-4dac-8732-8baa850a962e/ASUS%20ExpertBook%20Ultra%20(Morn%20Grey%20and%20Jet%20Fog).jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=asus.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">press.asus.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus comes to CES 2026 with an 'Ultra' ExpertBook built for the modern ...\" src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XNjxbmDaKQ9Sw3Dum7oFsi.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=itpro.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🖥️ ASUS ExpertBook Ultra (2026) — Full Review</h2>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><em>The Ultra-Premium Business Laptop That Changes Everything</em></h4>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n \n<div data-block=\"gutenkit/heading\" data-post-id=\"4361\" class=\"wp-block-gutenkit-heading gkit-heading-border-position-start gkitb20d12 gutenkit-block\" id=\"block-18beaffc-17e4-41b9-886f-296f15b20d12\"><h2 class=\"gkit-heading-title\">🇺🇸 Available Now in the USA — Buy on Amazon Today</h2><div class=\"gkit-heading-separetor gkit-heading-separetor-after-title gkit-heading-separetor-style-dotted\"><div class=\"gkit-heading-separetor-divider\"></div></div></div>\n \n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Where to Buy in the USA — ASUS ExpertBook Options on Amazon</h3>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">✅ <strong>Update: The ASUS ExpertBook Ultra (B9406CAA-XSP76T)</strong> with Intel Panther Lake — the flagship model reviewed above — <strong>is now available on Amazon.com USA</strong>, in both colorways covered in this review. Direct purchase links below.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🥇 ExpertBook Ultra B9406 — Now on Amazon USA</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The exact flagship model reviewed above — 32GB RAM, 1TB SSD, Intel Core Ultra X7 358H — is now shipping in the US, available in both colorways covered in this review.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Config</th><th>RAM</th><th>Storage</th><th>Color</th><th>Amazon Link</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Standard</td><td>32GB</td><td>1TB SSD</td><td>Jet Fog</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H42NWW8K?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">🛒 Buy on Amazon USA</a></td></tr><tr><td>Standard</td><td>32GB</td><td>1TB SSD</td><td>Morn Gray</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0H39NNXWG?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">🛒 Buy on Amazon USA</a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><em>Note: this is a newly-listed US launch, so review counts are still low — the ratings will build up over the coming weeks. All specs and performance details above are from independent reviewer testing and ASUS&#8217;s own published specifications, not from this listing.</em></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🥇 Best Alternative Available NOW — ASUS ExpertBook B9 OLED</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The <strong>ASUS ExpertBook B9 OLED (B9403CVA)</strong> is the direct predecessor to the Ultra — and it&#8217;s an exceptional laptop in its own right. Same premium ASUS business DNA, same featherlight philosophy, and available for immediate purchase on Amazon USA today.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it&#8217;s still a great buy:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>✅ Ultralight at just <strong>2.18 lbs</strong> — one of the lightest 14&#8243; business laptops available</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Stunning <strong>14-inch 2.8K (2880 × 1800) OLED HDR display</strong> with 16:10 aspect ratio</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Aerospace-grade <strong>magnesium-lithium alloy</strong> chassis with MIL-STD-810H certification</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Blazing fast <strong>PCIe NVMe M.2 SSD</strong> storage</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ All-day battery life with fast charging</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Enterprise-grade security built in</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Choose your configuration:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Config</th><th>RAM</th><th>Storage</th><th>Color</th><th>Amazon Link</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Standard</td><td>16GB</td><td>1TB SSD</td><td>Star Black</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CDM73J2Q?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">🛒 Buy on Amazon USA</a></td></tr><tr><td>Premium</td><td>32GB</td><td>2TB SSD</td><td>Star Black</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CDMC2F28?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">🛒 Buy on Amazon USA</a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🆕 Also Available — ASUS ExpertBook P5 (2026 Copilot+ AI Laptop)</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">If you want the very latest 2026 ASUS technology that&#8217;s <strong>available on Amazon right now</strong>, the <strong>ExpertBook P5</strong> is the one to get. It&#8217;s a brand-new Copilot+ AI laptop built for modern professionals who need on-device AI performance without waiting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>✅ <strong>Copilot+ PC</strong> certified — Microsoft&#8217;s highest AI-readiness standard</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Intel Core Ultra Series processors with dedicated <strong>AI NPU</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ <strong>2.5K 144Hz display</strong> — sharper and smoother than standard business panels</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Wi-Fi 7, Thunderbolt 4, HDMI 2.1</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Sleek <strong>Misty Grey</strong> finish — modern and professional</li>\n\n\n\n<li>✅ Competitively priced below the Ultra</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Choose your configuration:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Config</th><th>RAM</th><th>Storage</th><th>Color</th><th>Amazon Link</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Core Ultra 5</td><td>16GB</td><td>512GB SSD</td><td>Misty Grey</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DJG3HK85?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">🛒 Buy on Amazon USA</a></td></tr><tr><td>Core Ultra 7</td><td>32GB</td><td>1TB SSD</td><td>Misty Grey</td><td><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DJG3HK85?tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">🛒 Buy on Amazon USA</a></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🔍 First Look — Stunning from Every Angle</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus comes to CES 2026 with an 'Ultra' ExpertBook built for the modern ...\" src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XNjxbmDaKQ9Sw3Dum7oFsi.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=itpro.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">itpro.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS Unveils 2026 AI-Powered Portfolio at CES, including ExpertBook ...\" src=\"https://www.glitched.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1.png\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=glitched.online&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">glitched.online</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Image unavailable</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The ASUS ExpertBook Ultra (B9406) launched in early 2026 and has already turned heads across the tech world. It weighs just <strong>0.99 kg</strong>, runs on Intel&#8217;s brand-new <strong>Panther Lake processor</strong>, and sports a gorgeous <strong>14-inch 3K Tandem OLED display</strong>. <a href=\"https://techreviewed.blog/asus-expertbook-ultra-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tech Reviewed</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The ExpertBook Ultra has more in common with ASUS&#8217;s thin-and-light Zenbook line than with previous ExpertBooks — it&#8217;s a gorgeous, ultra-thin machine built for business but designed to look good doing it. <a href=\"https://www.itpro.com/hardware/laptops/the-asus-expertbook-ultra-is-a-gorgeous-ultra-thin-laptop-that-houses-a-killer-intel-panther-lake-processor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IT Pro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🏗️ Design &amp; Build Quality</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS launches its flagship business laptop, the ExpertBook Ultra, with ...\" src=\"https://p1.toutiaoimg.com/origin/tos-cn-i-tjoges91tu/6badb6e4d9767d09bd2df26954acce57.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=min.news&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">min.news<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS launches its flagship business laptop, the ExpertBook Ultra, with ...\" src=\"https://p1.toutiaoimg.com/origin/tos-cn-i-tjoges91tu/03fa0be646c4b129053cb90b7a5d5c50.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=min.news&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">min.news<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS Unveils 2026 AI-Powered Portfolio at CES, including ExpertBook ...\" src=\"https://www.glitched.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/6.png\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=glitched.online&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">glitched.online</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The chassis is machined from <strong>AZ31B magnesium-aluminum alloy</strong> — an aerospace-grade material — weighing just 0.99 kg at only <strong>10.9 mm thin</strong>, protected by a <strong>9H Nano Ceramic coating</strong> that resists scratches and stains. <a href=\"https://www.asus.com/laptops/for-work/expertbook/asus-expertbook-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asus</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The &#8220;Morn Gray&#8221; colorway is modern and professional — with a matte finish and metallic luster that sparkles in the right light. A darker <strong>Jet Fog</strong> variant is also available. <a href=\"https://www.pcworld.com/article/3044102/asus-expertbook-ultra-review.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">PCWorld</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The body feels more rigid than its predecessors, yet even slimmer — easy to pick up one-handed and slip into a bag — while passing <strong>MIL-STD-810H</strong> certification across 24 durability procedures. <a href=\"https://www.itpro.com/hardware/laptops/the-asus-expertbook-ultra-is-a-gorgeous-ultra-thin-laptop-that-houses-a-killer-intel-panther-lake-processor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IT Pro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">⚡ Performance — Intel Panther Lake Inside</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Intel Core Ultra Series 3 “Panther Lake” debuts at CES 2026 | migovi\" src=\"https://migovi.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/intel-core-ultra-series-3-panther-lake-ces-2026-family-lineup.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=migovi.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">migovi.com</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Image unavailable<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Intel Core Ultra Series 3 Processors CES 2026 Launch: AI, Gaming, Xe ...\" src=\"https://internationalnewsandviews.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/intel-core-ultra-series-3-p.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=internationalnewsandviews.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">internationalnewsandviews.com</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The ExpertBook Ultra runs on the <strong>Intel Core Ultra X7 358H</strong> from the Panther Lake family — <strong>16 cores, 16 threads</strong>, boosting up to 4.8 GHz, with an AI NPU delivering <strong>50 TOPS</strong>. Apps open instantly, browser tabs load without hesitation, and multitasking feels completely seamless. <a href=\"https://techreviewed.blog/asus-expertbook-ultra-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tech Reviewed</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Panther Lake represents a generational leap over Lunar Lake and Arrow Lake — particularly in GPU performance-per-watt — while fitting inside a sub-1 kg, 14-inch laptop body. <a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Asus-ExpertBook-Ultra-review-One-helluva-debut-for-Intel-Panther-Lake-X7.1209366.0.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Notebookcheck</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">ASUS claims the integrated <strong>Intel Arc B390 graphics outperforms a dedicated NVIDIA RTX 4050 at 30W TGP by approximately 35%</strong> in 3DMark Time Spy — a remarkable achievement for an integrated GPU. <a href=\"https://www.gadgetbridge.com/news/asus-launches-expertbook-ultra-in-india-a-sub-1kg-ai-business-laptop/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gadget Bridge</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The laptop is also among the first consumer devices to ship with a <strong>PCIe Gen 5 NVMe SSD</strong>, hitting sequential read speeds of up to <strong>14,090 MB/s</strong> — roughly double what PCIe Gen 4 drives can manage. <a href=\"https://www.gadgetbridge.com/news/asus-launches-expertbook-ultra-in-india-a-sub-1kg-ai-business-laptop/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gadget Bridge</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🖥️ Display — Tandem OLED Brilliance</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus comes to CES 2026 with an 'Ultra' ExpertBook built for the modern ...\" src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XNjxbmDaKQ9Sw3Dum7oFsi.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=itpro.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">itpro.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus Unveils New ExpertBook Ultra Ultraportable With Tandem OLED Screen ...\" src=\"https://highperformancelaptops.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ExpertBook-Ultra_B9406CAA-front-view-1024x683.webp\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=highperformancelaptops.com.au&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">highperformancelaptops.com.au<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Heyup News |ASUS Unveils the ExpertBook Ultra: A Featherlight ...\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0653/9958/7054/files/imgi_179_s7w8kyzxEihJBHRvHbtEeG.jpg?v=1769580826\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=heyupnow.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">heyupnow.com</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The <strong>14-inch Tandem OLED panel</strong> at a <strong>2880 x 1800 (3K)</strong> resolution in a <strong>16:10 aspect ratio</strong> delivers pin-sharp clarity, vibrant contrast, and wide color — equally at home handling spreadsheets, high-resolution images, or 4K media. The stacked Tandem OLED layers provide triple the brightness and 40% lower power consumption than standard OLEDs. <a href=\"https://www.itpro.com/hardware/laptops/the-asus-expertbook-ultra-is-a-gorgeous-ultra-thin-laptop-that-houses-a-killer-intel-panther-lake-processor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IT Pro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Maximum brightness reaches an extraordinary <strong>1,403 nits in HDR mode</strong> — while most OLEDs on competing laptops top out at roughly half that figure. <a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Asus-ExpertBook-Ultra-review-One-helluva-debut-for-Intel-Panther-Lake-X7.1209366.0.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Notebookcheck</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The screen holds <strong>Pantone validation</strong> — rare for a business laptop — making it fully capable for creative and color-accurate workflows, not just spreadsheets and presentations. <a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/computing/asus-expertbook-ultra-2026-business-laptop-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TechRadar</a></p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">⚠️ Minor caveat: the matte Gorilla Glass overlay introduces slight graininess compared to glossy OLED panels, which some users may notice on bright white content. <a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Asus-ExpertBook-Ultra-review-One-helluva-debut-for-Intel-Panther-Lake-X7.1209366.0.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Notebookcheck</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">⌨️ Keyboard, Trackpad &amp; Audio</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ASUS Unveils 2026 AI-Powered Portfolio at CES, including ExpertBook ...\" src=\"https://www.glitched.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1.png\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=glitched.online&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">glitched.online<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus comes to CES 2026 with an 'Ultra' ExpertBook built for the modern ...\" src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XNjxbmDaKQ9Sw3Dum7oFsi.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=itpro.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">itpro.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus ExpertBook B3 review: The powerful office laptop with 11-hour ...\" src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/_processed_/1/2/csm_Asus_ExpertBook_B3_B3404CVF_Keyboard_b648e1b872.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=notebookcheck.net&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">notebookcheck.net</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The keyboard delivers a light yet firm action with satisfying tactile response and zero deck flex — one of the finest typing experiences on any thin-and-light Windows laptop available today. <a href=\"https://www.itpro.com/hardware/laptops/the-asus-expertbook-ultra-is-a-gorgeous-ultra-thin-laptop-that-houses-a-killer-intel-panther-lake-processor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IT Pro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The expansive haptic touchpad spans nearly the full width of the deck, with a perfectly smooth glass surface and flawless tracking accuracy. <a href=\"https://www.itpro.com/hardware/laptops/the-asus-expertbook-ultra-is-a-gorgeous-ultra-thin-laptop-that-houses-a-killer-intel-panther-lake-processor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IT Pro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The <strong>six-speaker system</strong> with dual magnetic woofers and dedicated tweeters delivers deep bass and a rich, wide soundstage — impressive for a machine this slim. <a href=\"https://www.asus.com/laptops/for-work/expertbook/asus-expertbook-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asus</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🔌 Connectivity &amp; Ports</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus comes to CES 2026 with an 'Ultra' ExpertBook built for the modern ...\" src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XNjxbmDaKQ9Sw3Dum7oFsi.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=itpro.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">itpro.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus ExpertBook Ultra Review\" src=\"https://tbreak.com/content/images/2026/02/IMG_4279.jpeg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=tbreak.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">tbreak.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Asus ExpertBook P5 P5405 laptop in review: Intel's M1 moment in a ...\" src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/_processed_/7/d/csm_DSC_0089_bdaf590122.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=notebookcheck.net&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">notebookcheck.net</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Despite its ultra-slim profile, the ExpertBook Ultra includes two <strong>Thunderbolt 4/USB-C</strong> ports, two <strong>USB 3.2 Gen 2</strong> Type-A ports, <strong>HDMI 2.1</strong>, and a <strong>3.5 mm audio jack</strong> — one of each on either side for balanced desktop-style connectivity. <a href=\"https://www.itpro.com/hardware/laptops/the-asus-expertbook-ultra-is-a-gorgeous-ultra-thin-laptop-that-houses-a-killer-intel-panther-lake-processor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">IT Pro</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Wi-Fi 7</strong> and <strong>Bluetooth 5.4</strong> handle wireless duties, while advanced <strong>Laser Direct Structuring</strong> antenna design improves wireless performance by up to 43%. <a href=\"https://www.asus.com/laptops/for-work/expertbook/asus-expertbook-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asus</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🔋 Battery Life</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The <strong>70Wh battery</strong> is rated for up to <strong>26 hours</strong> of use, with <strong>90W USB-C fast charging</strong> reaching 50% capacity in just 30 minutes. <a href=\"https://www.fonearena.com/blog/480908/asus-expertbook-ultra-expertbook-p3-p5-series-price-india-features.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Fone Arena</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Real-world reviewer testing shows between <strong>15 and 21 hours</strong> — still class-leading for a productivity laptop of this caliber. <a href=\"https://techreviewed.blog/asus-expertbook-ultra-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tech Reviewed</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🔐 Enterprise Security</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The ExpertBook Ultra features <strong>Microsoft Pluton</strong> — a security processor built into the CPU itself — alongside <strong>Windows Secured-core PC</strong> compliance and <strong>NIST SP 800-193-certified</strong> firmware protection, delivering enterprise-grade security out of the box from the very first boot. <a href=\"https://www.asus.com/laptops/for-work/expertbook/asus-expertbook-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Asus</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🤝 How Does It Compare?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"This Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon Gen 13 deal sees 14-inch OLED business ...\" src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/_processed_/e/7/csm_thinkpad_X1Carbon_G13_teaser_0f8e63269f.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=notebookcheck.net&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">notebookcheck.net<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The 10 best laptops at CES 2026 | PCWorld\" src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Lenovo-ThinkPad-X1-Carbon-Aura-Edition-at-CES-2026.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=pcworld.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">pcworld.com<img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Lenovo unveils ThinkPad X1 laptops with Intel Core Ultra | Windows Central\" src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dPYYEkXN6uryfQeNL2vsBX.jpg\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=windowscentral.com&amp;sz=32\" alt=\"\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">windowscentral.com</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">6</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://support.claude.com/en/articles/13641943-visual-and-interactive-content\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Results from the web</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th><strong>ASUS ExpertBook Ultra</strong></th><th><strong>Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon</strong></th><th><strong>HP EliteBook Ultra G1i</strong></th><th><strong>Apple MacBook Pro M4</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Weight</td><td><strong>0.99 kg ✅</strong></td><td>~1.12 kg</td><td>~1.14 kg</td><td>~1.55 kg</td></tr><tr><td>Display</td><td><strong>3K Tandem OLED ✅</strong></td><td>14&#8243; IPS/OLED</td><td>2.8K OLED</td><td>Liquid Retina XDR</td></tr><tr><td>Processor</td><td><strong>Intel Panther Lake X7/X9 ✅</strong></td><td>Intel Core Ultra Series 2</td><td>Intel Core Ultra Series 2</td><td>Apple M4</td></tr><tr><td>iGPU</td><td><strong>Arc B390 (RTX 4050 class) ✅</strong></td><td>Intel iGPU</td><td>Intel iGPU</td><td>Apple GPU</td></tr><tr><td>SSD Speed</td><td><strong>PCIe Gen 5 — 14,090 MB/s ✅</strong></td><td>PCIe Gen 4</td><td>PCIe Gen 4</td><td>Apple SSD</td></tr><tr><td>Battery (rated)</td><td><strong>26 hrs ✅</strong></td><td>~15 hrs</td><td>~14 hrs</td><td>~22 hrs</td></tr><tr><td>India Warranty</td><td><strong>5 years (launch) ✅</strong></td><td>3 years</td><td>1–3 years</td><td>1 year</td></tr><tr><td>India Price</td><td>₹2,39,990</td><td>~₹2,20,000+</td><td>~₹1,90,000+</td><td>₹2,19,900+</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">ASUS itself positions the ExpertBook Ultra directly against the <strong>Lenovo ThinkPad X1 Carbon</strong> and <strong>Dell Pro 14 Premium</strong> — two laptops that regularly command around $2,500 when similarly configured. <a href=\"https://www.pcworld.com/article/3044102/asus-expertbook-ultra-review.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">PCWorld</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Heavier machines like the <strong>HP ZBook Ultra G1a</strong> (AMD Strix Halo) can edge ahead in raw CPU horsepower, but they do so at a much higher power draw and greater weight — a trade-off that defeats the purpose for road warriors. <a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Asus-ExpertBook-Ultra-review-One-helluva-debut-for-Intel-Panther-Lake-X7.1209366.0.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Notebookcheck</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">✅ Pros &amp; ❌ Cons</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>✅ Pros</th><th>❌ Cons</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Sub-1 kg aerospace-grade build</td><td>No discrete GPU for heavy 3D work</td></tr><tr><td>1,400-nit Tandem OLED — best in class</td><td>Matte coating causes slight graininess</td></tr><tr><td>RTX 4050-class integrated graphics</td><td>No SD card slot or Ethernet</td></tr><tr><td>PCIe Gen 5 SSD — fastest available</td><td>Haptic trackpad can be oversensitive</td></tr><tr><td>5-year India warranty (launch offer)</td><td>Real battery life below ASUS&#8217;s 26-hr claim</td></tr><tr><td>20 dB whisper-quiet cooling</td><td>Premium price — not for casual users</td></tr><tr><td>Microsoft Pluton enterprise security</td><td>RAM is soldered, not upgradeable</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🏁 Final Verdict</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The ASUS ExpertBook Ultra is one of the best business laptops of 2026, delivering a rare combination of featherweight portability, outstanding battery life, a brilliant OLED display, and strong Intel Panther Lake performance. For professionals who value lightness without compromise, this laptop sets a new standard and is genuinely the one to beat in 2026&#8217;s premium business segment. <a href=\"https://techreviewed.blog/asus-expertbook-ultra-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tech Reviewed</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">⭐ Rating: <strong>9.2 / 10</strong></h4>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🇮🇳 Available in India — Now on Flipkart!</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The ASUS ExpertBook Ultra has officially launched in India, with pre-orders live on Flipkart at a starting price of <strong>₹2,39,990</strong>. Unveiled at a launch event in Delhi on April 22, 2026, it is one of the most technically ambitious business laptops to land in the country this year. Buyers using an <strong>Axis Bank card</strong> can get an additional <strong>₹20,000 off</strong> on purchase. <a href=\"https://www.gadgetbridge.com/news/asus-launches-expertbook-ultra-in-india-a-sub-1kg-ai-business-laptop/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Gadget Bridge</a><a href=\"https://telecomtalk.info/asus-expertbook-ultra-launched-in-india-price/1006620/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">TelecomTalk</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Pre-order launch benefits include a <strong>5-year onsite warranty</strong>, <strong>5-year battery warranty</strong>, and <strong>5-year accidental damage protection</strong> worth ₹12,190. <a href=\"https://www.fonearena.com/blog/480908/asus-expertbook-ultra-expertbook-p3-p5-series-price-india-features.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Fone Arena</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">🛒 <strong>The ASUS ExpertBook Ultra is available NOW in India exclusively on Flipkart, starting at ₹2,39,990.</strong> Pre-order benefits including 5-year warranty coverage and ₹20,000 Axis Bank discount are live until <strong>29th April 2026.</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">👉 <strong>[Buy on Flipkart via ChampionsReviews.Com]</strong> | <strong>[See More Deals on ToolsShopy.Store]</strong></p>\n<